N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 462.3 - Transmittal and filing

State Regulations

Copies of all decisions and of all revisions thereof shall
be sent promptly to the commissioner and to all other parties affected thereby
and shall be filed promptly in the department at a place designated by the
commissioner. Notes
